'''The Barrows''' was the name of a large graveyard on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Trulalis]]. The graveyard was on the outskirts of the [[Kovit]] settlement and contained the victims of a massacre by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] troops. After returning to Trulalis to find the Kovit settlement destroyed, [[Adalric Cessius Brandl]] created The Barrows to honor his former friends and family who had died because of him. The Imperial troops that had massacred the town had been searching for him. The Barrows also contained an elaborate grave for Adalric's wife who died defending their son, [[Jaalib Brandl]] from [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]].<ref name="Uhl Eharl Khoehng">{{JournalCite|8|Uhl Eharl Khoehng (short story)}}</ref>

